{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Dog of Flanders is an adventure game based on the novel of the same name by the British author Ouida. The game is set in Belgium at the end of the 19th century during the first industrial revolution. The player takes on the role of Nello, a poor boy in a small village near Antwerp, who is starving but who paints as his faith and means of survival. Will his dream be realised in the harsh reality of his life? Together with the protagonist, the player will go through an unforgettable journey.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players can decide for themselves the order in which they want to experience the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/f6.gif?t=1733712787\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different choices will have different effects on the direction of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/f7.gif?t=1733712787\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel free to create your own paintings in various parts of the game world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/f3.gif?t=1733712787\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the beautiful scenery of the Flanders region of Belgium.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/f1.gif?t=1733712787\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the unique atmosphere of 19th century Flanders, Belgium.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/f4.gif?t=1733712787\" />